=Veil of Revenge=
=Episode 6=

13
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:04,070
Honey!

14
00:01:05,510 --> 00:01:06,350
Hello?

15
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:07,470
You can't.

16
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,590
You can't.

17
00:02:29,290 --> 00:02:30,190
It turns out

18
00:02:30,790 --> 00:02:31,830
I'm not the reason

19
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,310
why we can't have a child.

20
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:37,270
I can't believe Zhiren has azoospermia.

21
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,950
He's been

22
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,230
lying to me for a year.

23
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,600
But all men

24
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,830
are proud.

25
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,950
He wouldn't

26
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,190
tell me the truth,

27
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,760
but

28
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,910
he's been so good to me.

29
00:02:53,850 --> 00:02:56,950
I believe he had no choice but to lie

30
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,870
because he couldn't face it.

31
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,550
He's also a poor guy.

32
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,990
Since I love him,

33
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,310
I should keep the secret for him.

34
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,510
It's okay if we can't have a child.

35
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,210
As long as we love each other,

36
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,710
we'll grow old together.

