(Farewell Letter)

38
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:30,100
(Beloved Wife Chen Yue)

39
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,470
The love of my life,

40
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,900
the woman who lit up my world,

41
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:42,980
(Beloved Wife Chen Yue)

42
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,470
my wife Chen Yue

43
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,870
has left me forever

44
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,870
because of depression.

45
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,230
I can't bear...

46
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,470
losing my dear Yue!

47
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:01,990
I'll remember her
for the rest of my life!

48
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,800
Zhiren.

49
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,740
Zhiren.

50
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:05,750
Zhiren!

51
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,680
Zhiren!

52
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,550
Why was Yue so silly?

53
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,990
Why would she end her life like this?

54
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,470
It's my fault.

55
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,790
It's all my fault!

56
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,390
Yue was too kind.

57
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,950
She didn't want me to worry about her,

58
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:23,390
so she never told me
about her depression.

59
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:25,920
Zhiren.

60
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,390
You've been

61
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,830
dealing with Yue's funeral

62
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,190
over the past few days.

63
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,510
Thank you!

64
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,150
Dad, Mom,

65
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,790
This is my duty.

66
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,670
Yue is gone,

67
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,550
but I'll take care of you for her.

68
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,790
We want

69
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,750
to go abroad to take a break.

70
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,280
Dad.

71
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:49,910
Dad.

72
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,710
I'll manage the company well.

73
