(One Year Later)

74
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,160
Wow.

75
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,830
After paying the bills,

76
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,310
you can leave the hospital.

77
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,790
It's been a tough six months.

78
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,440
Yes.

79
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:53,020
Thank you for taking care of me.

80
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,220
It's our job.

81
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:56,070
You're welcome.

82
00:06:56,410 --> 00:06:58,350
You're the one who suffered a lot.

83
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,150
Luckily, the surgery was successful,

84
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,640
and you've lost weight.

85
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,670
You're so pretty now.

86
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,550
Come on. Here it is.

87
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,920
Take a look.

88
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,070
To be clear,

89
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,270
You can only make

90
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,710
monthly payments for three months.

91
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,110
When you get a job,

92
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,510
you need to pay the rent

93
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,110
every three months.

94
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,470
It'll also save you some money.

95
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,480
Okay.

96
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,790
Okay. Unpack your things.

97
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,640
I'm leaving.

98
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,600
Feel free to call me.

99
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:36,920
Okay, thanks.

100
